Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟 来接我和Amy的车2分钟内就到了\N{\fs38}Ok, duke, car's picking me and Amy up in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定能在我坐游轮的时候帮我跟着点我的案子\N{\fs38}You sure you're cool keeping tabs on my cases while I'm on the cruise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 你要玩得开心哦\N{\fs38}You bet. I hope you have a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 但是别交新的好朋友\N{\fs38}Hey, don't make any new best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 也许你就不该去\N{\fs38}Oh. Maybe you shouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吗 我想去这个一周游轮行都想疯了\N{\fs38}Are you kidding? I am psyched to go on this week-long cruise,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 就坐在那无所事事\N{\fs38} just sitting around doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着懒洋洋的惬意生活咯 \N{\fs38}Straight up living that slug life, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新鲜出炉的游轮活动项目哦\N{\fs38}Cruise itineraries, hot out of the laminator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁准备好享受毫不停歇安排满满的欢乐时光了\N{\fs38}Who's ready for some nonstop totally scheduled fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我其实想的我们就 坐在水边\N{\fs38}Oh, I actually thought we could just...sit by the pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃着无限量的虾 看看身体能有什么变化\N{\fs38}eat unlimited shrimp, and see what it does to our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.62,0:00:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得不错\N{\fs38}That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不知道时间够不够\N{\fs38}I don't know if there's gonna be time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次航游提供77种活动\N{\fs38}The cruise offers 77 activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给我们俩报名参加了76个\N{\fs38}and I signed us up for 76 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.34,0:00:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个寡妇速配相亲好像蛮晦气的\N{\fs38}Speed dating for widows seemed like a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 对这次游轮旅行有一点点\N{\fs38}Okay, so slightly different perspectives
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同看法哦\N{\fs38}going into this cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫惬意生活话题\N{\fs38}Call it the slug life talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我觉得这事船到桥头自然直\N{\fs38}but I think it's gonna work itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见咯 同事们\N{\fs38}Good-bye, coworkers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者像在海上说话那样\N{\fs38}or as they like to say at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这太棒了  - 是呀\N{\fs38}- This is so great. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鸥 有了\N{\fs38}Seagulls, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海 有了\N{\fs38}The ocean, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群穿超短裤的老年人\N{\fs38}A gang of oldies in short shorts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在这儿了\N{\fs38}check, check, check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝对在游轮上了\N{\fs38}We are definitely on a cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎登船\N{\fs38}Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说"我爱旋转木马国际游轮有限责任公司"\N{\fs38}Say, "I love Carousel Cruises International Ltd."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我爱旋转木马国际游轮有限公司  - 我可不想说\N{\fs38}- I love Carousel Cruises International Ltd.  - I don't want to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs38}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远航派对在1小时后\N{\fs38}So...the Sail Away party is in an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 我安排了咱们去全龄钢琴酒吧\N{\fs38}and until then, I have us scheduled to take in live music
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听现场音乐会\N{\fs38}at the all-ages piano lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧 或者我们可以直接去房间\N{\fs38}Okay, okay. Or we could just head straight to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了塑料布所以我们可以在床上吃虾了\N{\fs38}I brought a plastic tarp so we can eat shrimp in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是全龄钢琴酒吧有无限量供应的玛格丽特哟\N{\fs38}But the all-ages piano lounge has bottomless margaritas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs38}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有加了土豆皮的饮料哦\N{\fs38}They also have a drink with a potato skin in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那就去这个全龄钢琴酒吧吧 尊敬的女士\N{\fs38}Ohh. To the all-ages piano lounge, merlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\fs38}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎登船 女士们先生们\N{\fs38}Welcome aboard, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是女士们\N{\fs38}but especially ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我熟悉这个声音\N{\fs38}I know that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好 现在是淫荡小黄曲时间\N{\fs38}Get ready. It's time for some smush songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Doug Judy 庞蒂亚克大盗\N{\fs38}Doug Judy. The Pontiac Bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在这\N{\fs38}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有关于暧昧的歌\N{\fs38}We got songs about smushing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有卿卿我我时听的歌\N{\fs38}songs for smushing to,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有给小孩子的歌\N{\fs38}songs for the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是全龄钢琴音乐酒吧\N{\fs38}This is the all-ages piano lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信他就在这 我追查了他好几年\N{\fs38}I can't believe he's here. I've been hunting him for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在命运把他送到我脚边了\N{\fs38}and now fate has dropped him right into my lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看见我肯定会很惊讶\N{\fs38}He's gonna be so surprised when he sees me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Peralta 你来啦\N{\fs38}Hey, Peralta, you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么那么久才来 兄弟\N{\fs38}What took you so long, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 看来他掩饰得挺好\N{\fs38}Okay, seems like he's playing it pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心肯定惊慌失措\N{\fs38}Probably more surprised on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\fs38}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.68,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(14.343,586.171,227.899,582.157,39,248)}{\fs45}99分局\N{\fs10}\N{\fs45}上午11:42
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 Gina和我都很担心你\N{\fs38}Sir, Gina and I are worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都在喝第二罐苏打水了\N{\fs38}You're drinking a second can of seltzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要它安抚我的紧张情绪\N{\fs38}I need this to settle my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飓风Debbie就要来了\N{\fs38}Hurricane Debbie is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妹妹Debbie 是个小题大做一惊一乍的女人\N{\fs38}My little sister Debbie, she's a real drama queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Holt家一惊一乍的女人\N{\fs38}The drama queen of the Holt family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 她是有一次笑得大声了吗\N{\fs38}What, did she laugh out loud one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她大声笑了太多次了\N{\fs38}She's laughed out loud multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 你定义一惊一乍的标准很低\N{\fs38}Sir, you have a pretty low bar for what you consider drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次我在邮件里用了感叹号\N{\fs38}Once, I used an exclamation point in a email.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.74,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Diana Ross 美国著名黑人女歌手\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就叫我Diana Ross\N{\fs38}You called me Diana Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证 在这件事上 我没有夸张\N{\fs38}I assure you, in this case, I do not exaggerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Raymond{\fs38}\NRaymond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fs38}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们自己判断吧\N{\fs38}Judge for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这呢\N{\fs38}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我的天啊\N{\fs38}Great. Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从火车站到这的路上\N{\fs38}My trip here from the train station--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证我绝对听到出租车司机\N{\fs38}hey, I swear to you I heard the cab driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘀嘀咕咕"你今晚会死"\N{\fs38}mumble under his breath, "You will die tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道不是你听到的最疯狂的事吗\N{\fs38}Is that not the most insane thing you have ever heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗 Raymond\N{\fs38}I mean, can you even, Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我简直 不能\N{\fs38}I cannot...even.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.10,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(14.343,586.171,227.899,582.157,39,248)}{\fs45}死亡调查\N{\fs10}\N{\fs45}下午1:36
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一段时间没看见她了\N{\fs38}I hadn't seen her in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一个人住\N{\fs38}She lived alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经89岁高龄\N{\fs38}She was 89 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢\N{\fs38}Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有强行入室痕迹和明显创伤\N{\fs38}There's no forced entry or visible trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大可能是自然死亡\N{\fs38}It's probably natural causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们会四处看看  - 当然\N{\fs38}- We'll take a look around. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个公寓真大\N{\fs38}This huge apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有多大 是不是有1800平方英尺\N{\fs38}What is this, like, 1,800 square feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裸露砖墙\N{\fs38}Exposed brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有极好的自然采光\N{\fs38}Got tons of natural light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 我以为你会对煤气灶更感兴趣\N{\fs38}Weird. I thought you'd be most exciting about the gas range.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还有煤气灶\N{\fs38}They have a gas range.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要申请这套公寓\N{\fs38}I have to apply for this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 这刚刚空出来\N{\fs38}I mean, it just became available.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们俩看见过\N{\fs38}We're the only two people to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你在纽约房产界\N{\fs38}This is an opportunity you just don't get
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年难遇的机会啊\N{\fs38}in New York real estate ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位女士刚刚在这死去\N{\fs38}A woman just died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么庸俗无礼\N{\fs38}Don't be gross and disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了个去 快看这个衣帽间\N{\fs38}Holy crap, look at all this closet space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要申请\N{\fs38}I'm applying too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你根本不需要衣帽间\N{\fs38}What? You don't need closet space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概只有 一件外套\N{\fs38}You have, like, one outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就让给我吧  - 不行\N{\fs38}- Just let me have this. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们同时看见的\N{\fs38}We saw it at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就最强者赢\N{\fs38}May the best man win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏开始\N{\fs38}Game on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳\N{\fs38}Eh-hem
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 联系下一位死者亲属的游戏\N{\fs38}I mean, the game of contacting the next of kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就喜欢玩这种游戏\N{\fs38}That's the game I like to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peralta 你在这艘船上可不是巧合\N{\fs38}Peralta, it's no coincidence you're on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没参加任何比赛就得到免费游轮票\N{\fs38}You won a free cruise without entering a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这是怎么回事儿\N{\fs38}How do you think that happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.13,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Speed 2 电影<生死时速2> 故事背景设定在豪华邮轮上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是我买了<生死时速2>来看\N{\fs38}Maybe it's because I bought "Speed 2" On DVD,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以互联网认定游轮\N{\fs38}and the Internet realized that cruises
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的爱好之一\N{\fs38}were one of my interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好电影 Sandy穿着纱裙\N{\fs38}Great film. Sandy B. in a sarong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太对了\N{\fs38}Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个票是我给的\N{\fs38}But the tix are all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你叫来是因为我有危险了\N{\fs38}I brought you here 'cause I'm in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 危险 \N{\fs38}Pfft. Peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许"切"我的危险\N{\fs38}Don't "Pfft" My peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切\N{\fs38}Pfft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要杀我 我需要保护\N{\fs38}Somebody's trying to kill me, and I need protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我叫来了我最好的朋友\N{\fs38}so I sent for my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你最好的朋友\N{\fs38}I am not your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你最大的敌人 你好好记住了\N{\fs38}I'm your worst enemy. Get that through your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的小打小闹\N{\fs38}It's this kind of bickering
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们成为这么可爱的一对\N{\fs38}that makes us such an adorable couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你怎么说 Judy 你被捕了\N{\fs38}Whatever, Judy. You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能逮捕我 兄弟 我们在公海上呢\N{\fs38}You can't arrest me, boo. We're in international waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样我想抽多少大麻就抽多少\N{\fs38}which is also why I can smoke as much weed as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到嗨爽之海哦\N{\fs38}Welcome to the high seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这不可能是真的\N{\fs38}No, no way that that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amy 告诉我我现在就能逮捕他\N{\fs38}Amy, tell me I can arrest him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Judy是对的 我们无权逮捕他\N{\fs38}Judy's right. We have no jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严格来说这艘船现在在乌兹别克斯坦管辖范围内\N{\fs38}Technically this boat flies under the flag of Uzbekistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦噢 你的姑娘很了解乌兹别克斯坦哟\N{\fs38}Uh-oh. Your girl knows about the Uzbeks. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是船长能逮捕他\N{\fs38}But the captain can have him arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这艘船上完全有这个权力\N{\fs38}He has total authority on this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 船长都爱我的\N{\fs38}Perfect. Captains love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就等着他或者她发现\N{\fs38}Just wait until he or she
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们雇佣了一个罪犯吧\N{\fs38}finds out they're employing a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多百分之四十的船员都是罪犯\N{\fs38}Yeah, about 40% of the crew are criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难找到想在船上生活的正常人\N{\fs38}It's hard to find normal people who want to live on a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己就是逃税者\N{\fs38}I, myself, am a tax evader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要在我们回到纽约前把他锁起来\N{\fs38}I just need him locked up till we get back to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能把他关在船上的监狱里吗\N{\fs38}Can't you just throw him in boat jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫船上禁闭室\N{\fs38}It's called the brig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我最棒的酒吧歌手\N{\fs38}He is my best lounge singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我得让乘客分心\N{\fs38}and I need to keep people distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我们之间说说 我们快没田园沙拉酱了\N{\fs38}Just between us, we're nearly out of ranch dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才第一天\N{\fs38}On day one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人简直就是动物\N{\fs38}These people are animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 只要他在我船上\N{\fs38}Listen, as long as he's on my boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Doug Judy就是自由的\N{\fs38}Doug Judy is a free man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jack Amy 欢迎到我的船舱\N{\fs38}Jake, Amy, welcome to my cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也叫做 砰砰豪华舱 \N{\fs38}AKA the Boom-Boom Stateroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs38}Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是皇室套房呀\N{\fs38}This is a royale level suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到我还能亲眼见到\N{\fs38}I never thought we'd see one in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是给旋转木马游轮年度艺人\N{\fs38}Little perk of being
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的特殊待遇\N{\fs38}Carousel Cruises' entertainer of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就是我哦 姑娘\N{\fs38}Which I am, girrr-rl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱走调了 \N{\fs38}A little pitch-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你们在这放松\N{\fs38}You're welcome to chill here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了感谢你们保护我 这是我能做的最起码的事了\N{\fs38}It's the least I can do to thank you for protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可能 这个保护骗局本身就是骗局\N{\fs38}Never. This protection scam is a scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的以为就因为你之前\N{\fs38}Do you honestly think you can fool me again
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功骗过我无数次了 就又能骗我一次吗\N{\fs38}just because you've successfully done it numerous times before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我以前的老大想让我死\N{\fs38}Look, my old boss wants me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在这艘船上隐姓埋名\N{\fs38}I've been laying low on this ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我从一个内部朋友那得到消息\N{\fs38}and I got word from a friend on the inside
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经找到我了 派了杀手\N{\fs38}that they found me, and there's a hitman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来结束我宝贵的生命\N{\fs38}coming to end my beautiful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会寄给你免费船票\N{\fs38}That's why I sent you the free tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 不可能 我不会信的\N{\fs38}No! No, no way. I'm not buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也不能从我这逃走\N{\fs38}You can't get away from me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amy和我在这次浪漫航行中的每一分每一秒\N{\fs38}Amy and I are gonna spend every second of our romantic cruise
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会盯紧你 可以吧\N{\fs38}watching you, assuming that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我们会这样做\N{\fs38}Yep. That's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能把这个活动计划丢一边了\N{\fs38}I'll just get rid of this itinerary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别别别 Amy 不要丢这个\N{\fs38}No, no, no, no, Ames, don't put that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得在这个杀手找到我前找到他\N{\fs38}We have to find the hitman before he finds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这个东西能带我们去船上每一个角落\N{\fs38}I'm guessing this'll take us all over the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦耶 这是角缝情况\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, that's an ENAC sitch right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"每个角落和缝隙"\N{\fs38}"Every Nook And Cranny."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美 我们会把这个坏人找遍每个角缝\N{\fs38}Perfect. We'll just ENAC sitch, uh, of this bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.86,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(14.343,586.171,227.899,582.157,39,248)}{\fs45}99分局\N{\fs10}\N{\fs45}上午11:42
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妹妹怎么样了 长官\N{\fs38}How's it going with your sister, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚她告诉我很多\N{\fs38}Well, last night, she told me in a great detail
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于她和她教练一场争吵的细节\N{\fs38}about a fight she got into with her trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说这个人偷了她的梳子\N{\fs38}whom she accused of stealing a hairbrush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在她正在电话里对着老妈大吼大叫\N{\fs38}Now she's on the phone, screaming at our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会把她支开的\N{\fs38}We'll keep her out of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对转移人注意力很在行\N{\fs38}I'm good at distracting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天都和孩子们这样\N{\fs38}It's what I do with my toddlers all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她对气球做的小动物感觉怎么样\N{\fs38}How does she feel about balloon animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确定她和它们有种复杂的关系\N{\fs38}I'm sure she has a complicated relationship with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ray  - 她来了\N{\fs38}- Ray! - Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要气球做的小动物\N{\fs38}No balloon animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不信老妈是怎么想的\N{\fs38}You ain't gonna believe mom's take on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她觉得我应该道歉\N{\fs38}She thinks I'm the one who should apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为最后梳子是在我车上\N{\fs38}just 'cause it turns out the hairbrush ended up being in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很乐意再讨论几次你梳子的事\N{\fs38}Yes, I'd love to discuss your hairbrush for even more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有些紧急的事情要处理\N{\fs38}but I have some pressing police matters to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你 大忙人\N{\fs38}Look at you. Always working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那个幽默的大哥哥去哪了\N{\fs38}What happened to my fun big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽默 我向来不幽默 把这话收回去\N{\fs38}Fun? I was never fun. You take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她不是这个意思\N{\fs38}I'm sure she didn't mean anything by it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在还小的时候 我们会跑去地下室\N{\fs38}When we were little, we would go down in the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他会给我们盖堡垒\N{\fs38}and he would build us a fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一待就是一整天\N{\fs38}We would stay down there all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ray会唱那些蠢蠢的自编歌曲\N{\fs38}And Ray would sing these silly little made-up songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:10.53,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,美国著名作曲家\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gershwin兄弟的歌可不是什么蠢蠢的瞎编的歌\N{\fs38}George and Ira Gershwin did not compose silly, made-up songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃Debbie 我带你在纽约转转吧\N{\fs38}Uh, Debbie, let me show you New York, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建筑啊 地铁啊 银行啊\N{\fs38}The buildings, the subway, the bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烘干机啊 我有事要去跑跑腿\N{\fs38}the dry cleaner-- I got to run some errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 Gina\N{\fs38}Oh, that's a great idea, Gina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Debbie 抱歉我没机会\N{\fs38}Debbie, I'm so sorry I won't get a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你来的时候多见见你\N{\fs38}to see you much on your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的\N{\fs38}Uh, no thing but a chicken wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我要在这待六周\N{\fs38}'cause I'm gonna be here for six weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要全身心地融入你的生活\N{\fs38}I'ma be all up in your life, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做完五个了\N{\fs38}I got five down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到主题了 是船\N{\fs38}I figured out the theme. It's boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好我明白了\N{\fs38}Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是聪明惹人爱 你是爆脾气惹人爱\N{\fs38}She's smart and lovable; you're scrappy and lovable;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个一起闪闪惹人爱\N{\fs38}together you're just lovable and lovable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个杀手在哪 Judy\N{\fs38}Okay, so where's this hitman, Judy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他们派谁来了\N{\fs38}Look, I don't know who they sent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他在船上\N{\fs38}but he's on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看这个旅客名单\N{\fs38}Check out this manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫Henry Coles的人在圣胡安登船\N{\fs38}Somebody boarded in San Juan named Henry Coles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Henry街和Coles街\N{\fs38}Henry Street and Coles Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你布鲁克林旧赃车行街角的两条街\N{\fs38}that's the corner of your old chop shop in Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是个化名  - 嗯哼\N{\fs38}- This is an alias. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的侍者哥儿们看了Henry Coles的客舱\N{\fs38}And my porter buddy checked out Henry Coles' cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还没住进去\N{\fs38}He hasn't been in it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他躲在这条船的某个地方\N{\fs38}He's hiding somewhere on this boat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻准备着出来杀我\N{\fs38}ready to jump out and kill me at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能就躲在我衣橱里\N{\fs38}Probably creepin' around in my closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 或者藏匿在救生艇里  - 或者躲在墙里\N{\fs38}- Or stowed away in a lifeboat. - Or hiding in a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者龟缩在轮机室\N{\fs38}Or holed up in the engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐蔽在灌木丛中\N{\fs38}Camouflaged in the shrubbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.23,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,美国<铁血战士>系列电影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掠夺者风格\N{\fs38}Predator style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们不是在玩\N{\fs38}No. We are not having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会被你的诡计所迷惑\N{\fs38}You will not suck me in with your wily charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gotaro先生 你的咖啡 加奶 没放糖\N{\fs38}Senor Gotaro, un cafe con leche, sin azucar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Gotaro先生 见到你很高兴\N{\fs38}Hola, Mr. Gotaro. Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和Rosa说句话吗\N{\fs38}Can I talk to Rosa for a quick sec
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是超级严肃的工作的事情\N{\fs38}about some super serious police work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你要干什么\N{\fs38}I know what you're trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把他搞来是为了巴结他\N{\fs38}You brought him in here to butter him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我已经做得\N{\fs38}Yeah, and I've been laying it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很夸张了\N{\fs38}real thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄荷糖\N{\fs38}Mint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你犯了个天大的错误\N{\fs38}Okay, but you're making a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人比Boyle还能跪舔巴结人\N{\fs38}Nobody sucks up like a Boyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你早就知道这个了因为你是聪明人\N{\fs38}Of course, you knew that already because you're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚对你使了这招\N{\fs38}I just did it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 小矮人\N{\fs38}Fine, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 上吧  - 好\N{\fs38}- Bring it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你和我\N{\fs38}Looks like you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来一场愉快的老派跪舔了\N{\fs38}are in a good, old-fashioned suck-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫它跪舔好吗\N{\fs38}Don't call it a suck-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不\N{\fs38}Why not? Why shouldn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢对对对对对\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 嗯哼 对 明智 好\N{\fs38}Totally, yep. Mm-hmm. Right. Smart. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自带了沙狐球的杆子\N{\fs38}You brought your own shuffleboard stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.52,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,tang也有阴道的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯哼  - 这叫做"球棍"\N{\fs38}- Mm-hmm. - They're called tangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该高兴她有自己的球棍\N{\fs38}You should be glad she has her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不想她用别的男人的"球棍"\N{\fs38}You don't want her messing with another man's tang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们不可能叫球棍吧\N{\fs38}There is no way they're called tangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这样\N{\fs38}It's true. They are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.96,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,biscuits有臀部的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙狐球的盘子叫做"饼干"\N{\fs38}And the disks are called biscuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是的  - "球棍"和"饼干"\N{\fs38}- Yes. - Tangs and biscuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无言以对\N{\fs38}That is so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正式爱上了沙狐球\N{\fs38}I officially love shuffleboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让出条路 我要抽打我的"饼干"了\N{\fs38}Clear a path! I'm about to whip my biscuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀\N{\fs38}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jake 你开心的时候\N{\fs38}About time you smiled, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是在强颜欢笑啊\N{\fs38}You've been a real tang in the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 嘿小建议\N{\fs38}- All right. - Hey, little advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amy很棒\N{\fs38}Amy is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想和她好下去\N{\fs38}You want to keep her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要接纳她的爱好\N{\fs38}be more receptive to her interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你扯太远了 Judy\N{\fs38}All right, now you're taking it too far, Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要罪犯死对头的感情建议\N{\fs38}I don't need relationship advice from my criminal archnemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想看到你们两个幸福\N{\fs38}Look, I just want to see you two happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这只是你的另一条谎言\N{\fs38}No. This is just another one of your lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和那个杀手的谎言一样\N{\fs38}just like your fake hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条船上有一个职业杀手\N{\fs38}There is a hitman on this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Henry Coles要来杀我\N{\fs38}Henry Coles is coming to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs38}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 你刚叫我名字了\N{\fs38}- What? - You said my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Henry Coles\N{\fs38}I'm Henry Coles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Henry Coles\N{\fs38}You're Henry Coles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的医疗腕带上写着呢\N{\fs38}According to my medical alert bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\fs38}Well, this is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Henry Coles 让我瞧瞧这个\N{\fs38}This is Henry Coles. Let's just take a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写着 "Doug Judy是骗子"\N{\fs38}Oh, it says, "Doug Judy is a liar."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实上面写的是 我有跌倒的风险\N{\fs38}Actually, it says I'm a fall risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你毁了我的梗 Henry\N{\fs38}Okay, you're kind of ruining my burn here, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fs38}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道Henry Coles是个\N{\fs38} I knew Henry Coles was a 90-year old man
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一型糖尿病和肺气肿的90岁老头\N{\fs38}with type 1 diabetes and emphysema.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显我不知道这么详细\N{\fs38}Obviously, I didn't know those specifics,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我早知道你在骗人\N{\fs38}but I knew you were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Henry Coles不是我们要找的人\N{\fs38}So Henry Coles wasn't the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的错\N{\fs38}My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有人在这条船上想杀我\N{\fs38}There's still somebody on this boat who wants to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想逍遥法外\N{\fs38}You're trying to get away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让这发生的\N{\fs38}and it's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的旅途我们要住在你的客舱里\N{\fs38}We're spending the rest of this trip in your cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amy和我轮流值班\N{\fs38}Amy and I will take sleep shifts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保时刻有人盯着你\N{\fs38}to make sure someone's always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 这让我觉得超级安全\N{\fs38}Thank you. That makes me feel super safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们想亲热 \N{\fs38}And if you want to smush,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有眼罩和隔音耳机\N{\fs38}I have a sleep mask and noise canceling headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能把他锁在里面吗\N{\fs38}Can't we just lock him up in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的要牺牲接下来六晚的睡眠吗\N{\fs38}Do we really have to trade off sleep for the next six nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 很抱歉\N{\fs38}I know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他说如果我们想亲热他会戴眼罩\N{\fs38}But he did say that he'd wear a mask if we want to smush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我明白了 他是庞蒂亚克大盗\N{\fs38}Fine. I get it. He's the Pontiac Bandit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先开始轮班\N{\fs38}You take the first shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 你最好了\N{\fs38}Thank you so much. You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 纽约警局 放了他\N{\fs38}Hey, NYPD! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你相信我了吗\N{\fs38}Now do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人要杀我\N{\fs38}That guy was trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 有人想让你死\N{\fs38}All right, fine! Someone wants you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了\N{\fs38}You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲亲 抱抱\N{\fs38}Smush, smush
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我听起来还是像个天使\N{\fs38}Ooh, I still sound like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定\N{\fs38}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢上帝你当时在 Peralta\N{\fs38}Thank God you were there, Peralta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你不会让最好的朋友死掉\N{\fs38}I knew you wouldn't let your best friend die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是要拘捕你 如果你死了我就不能了\N{\fs38}I'm still gonna arrest you. I just can't do that if you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你怎么自欺欺人\N{\fs38}Whatever you gotta tell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来 让他好好说话可真难\N{\fs38}Baby steps. It's hard getting him out of his shell.
