Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你妈 死猪\N{\fs38}Screw you, pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话太不老少咸宜了\N{\fs38}That is not a very all-ages thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是完全没有进入这里的气氛\N{\fs38}You just don't get the vibe here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 把那个绳子拿来\N{\fs38}Nice, grab that cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他绑起来 过来\N{\fs38}Let's get his arms. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被我女朋友"棍打"啦\N{\fs38}You just got tanged by my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我知道听起来很恶心\N{\fs38}Sorry, I know that sounded really gross,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上是很赞的\N{\fs38}but it was actually awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧Judy\N{\fs38}You okay, Judy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Judy\N{\fs38}Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不不不不不\N{\fs38}No. No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见Peralta 谢谢你救了我的命\N{\fs38}Bye, Peralta. Thanks for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不Judy 不要这样\N{\fs38}No. Judy! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要再耍我一次\N{\fs38}No, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Judy Judy\N{\fs38}Judy! Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Judy在哪 这船上所有地方我都找了\N{\fs38}Where is Judy? I've looked everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定在这船上的某个地方\N{\fs38}He has to be somewhere on this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peralta\N{\fs38}Peralta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他不在\N{\fs38}No, he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我这样对你 伙计\N{\fs38}Sorry to do this to you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见一个空档 不得不抓住了\N{\fs38}I saw an opening, and I had to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能进监狱 我太酷\N{\fs38}I can't go to jail. I'm too cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远也不会放过你的 Judy\N{\fs38}You'll never get away from me, Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不见你在说什么\N{\fs38} can't hear what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你离我太远了\N{\fs38}You're real far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就假装你终于承认了\N{\fs38}I'll just assume you're finally admitting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是最好的朋友\N{\fs38}we're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没有说那个\N{\fs38}No, that is not what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 这对我来说真的很重要\N{\fs38}Thank you. It means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受你的航海之旅把\N{\fs38}Enjoy the rest of your cruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住哦 你找到了一个好女人\N{\fs38}Just remember, you got a fine lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要强颜欢笑\N{\fs38}Don't be a tang in the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你的口袋\N{\fs38}Check your pockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰豪华舱 亲爱的\N{\fs38}Boom-Boom Stateroom, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs38}Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我跟你还没完\N{\fs38}But this isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要追捕你到地球尽头\N{\fs38}I will hunt you to the ends of the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fs38}I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能说出来我真的很骄傲\N{\fs38}I'm so proud of us for being able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还站在那里干什么\N{\fs38}What are you still standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 去干柴烈火吧 - Judy\N{\fs38}- Go smush! - Judy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但我的火车还有45分钟就开了\N{\fs38}Well, okay, but my train is in 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要非得过来说再见吧\N{\fs38}I don't have to say good-bye to Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想给他压力\N{\fs38}I don't want to stress him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他特意让我们叫你过来的\N{\fs38}No, he specifically asked us to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Debbie\N{\fs38}Hello, Debbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搭了堡垒\N{\fs38}You made a fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们可以在这儿聊聊\N{\fs38}I thought we could talk under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你和Gary的事儿\N{\fs38}about you and Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但\N{\fs38}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我想要把你赶走\N{\fs38}I'm sorry I was pushing you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你知道我一直在你身边\N{\fs38}I want you to know that I'm here for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常愿意参与你的人生\N{\fs38}and I would love to be all up in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你啊\N{\fs38}Aw, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快给我个拥抱  - 好\N{\fs38}- Give me a hug. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs38}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gotaro先生\N{\fs38}Mr. Gotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因涉嫌谋杀你的租户被逮捕了Shirley Crouch\N{\fs38}You're under arrest for the murder of your tenant Shirley Crouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我没把房子租给你们吗\N{\fs38}Is this because I didn't rent to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs38}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这却很可疑\N{\fs38}But that was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不愿意租给信誉可靠的警察呢\N{\fs38}Why wouldn't you want cops with great credit living in your building?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信用好还能买到鳗鱼\N{\fs38}Great credit and an eel hookup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你杀了她\N{\fs38}Because you murdered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒理学分析这位女士被投了毒\N{\fs38}Toxicology report says the old lady was poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的公寓有租金管制 你不能抬高租金\N{\fs38}Her apartment was rent controlled, and you couldn't jack up the price
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非她搬走\N{\fs38}until she was out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有最后一个问题\N{\fs38}I just have one last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你进监狱了 这里谁负责\N{\fs38}If you go to jail, who makes the rental decisions in the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给信托人\N{\fs38}It'll pass to a trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由银行负责\N{\fs38}The bank controls it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏继续\N{\fs38}Game back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还用问 那你已经落后了\N{\fs38}If you have to ask, you're already one step behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还得把他带回警局\N{\fs38}I should help bring him back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们还是警察  - 没错\N{\fs38}- We're still police officers. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 能问你个事儿吗\N{\fs38}Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs38}- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个厕所是冲到大海里的\N{\fs38}If the toilets drain into the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不是小鲨鱼就能游上来咬我屁股呢\N{\fs38}does that mean a tiny shark could swim up and bite me in the butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全不能\N{\fs38}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 真无聊  - 这样吧\N{\fs38}- Psh, lame. - Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道因为庞蒂亚克大盗的事情你很沮丧\N{\fs38}I know you're bummed about the Pontiac Bandit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这算是安慰的话\N{\fs38}so if it's any consolation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以剩下的时间\N{\fs38}we could spend the rest of the cruise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都躺在床上吃大虾\N{\fs38}eating shrimp in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那简直是棒呆 但是不要\N{\fs38}That is incredibly sweet, but no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要参加的活动太多了\N{\fs38}We have too many activities to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定猜不到三分钟之后是什么活动吧\N{\fs38}Eh? You'll never guess what starts in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 莎莎舞  - 哦 所以你能猜到\N{\fs38}- Salsa dancing. - Oh, so you can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs38}Thank you for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs38}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尊棒 冲明\N{\fs38}Noice. Smort.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fs38}I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我非常肯定\N{\fs38}Also, I think this is definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是孤寡老人的舞蹈课\N{\fs38}a dance class for widows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 我觉得不是  - 不是吗\N{\fs38}- No, I don't think so. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在转向你的舞伴告诉对方你的伴侣是如何去世的\N{\fs38}Now turn to your partner and tell them how your spouse died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该走了\N{\fs38}Yeah, we should get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你确定吗  - 确定\N{\fs38}- Are you sure? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}OK.
